serious talk with him.

52
00:06:05,541 --> 00:06:07,776
Mrs Fanning, we've had the talks.

53
00:06:07,876 --> 00:06:09,484
We've had the sessions
with the counsellor.

54
00:06:09,584 --> 00:06:13,351
