employ a monitor for him.

55
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:14,942
Monitor?

56
00:06:15,042 --> 00:06:16,900
He'll be separated from
the other children.

57
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:19,734
The monitor will supervise
him one-on-one.

58
00:06:19,834 --> 00:06:21,108
Samuel won't cope with this.

59
00:06:21,208 --> 00:06:22,567
