He got killed driving Mum
to the hospital to have me.

89
00:07:46,918 --> 00:07:48,118
Samuel.

90
00:07:49,626 --> 00:07:50,943
I'm sorry. He just...

91
00:07:51,043 --> 00:07:53,818
No, that's alright.
I shouldn't have...

92
00:07:53,918 --> 00:07:56,943
Well, your mum is very lucky
to have you, then, isn't she?

93
00:07:57,043 --> 00:07:58,477
We have to go.

94
00:07:58,835 --> 00:08:01,868
- Say, "See you later," Katie.
- Bye.

95
00:08:02,209 --> 00:08:04,026
The artist was so drunk, he vomited.

96
00:08:04,126 --> 00:08:05,693
Right in front of his
own installation.

97
00:08:05,793 --> 00:08:07,693
Lost all these sales.

98
00:08:07,793 --> 00:08:09,693
You're not listening.

99
00:08:09,835 --> 00:08:11,068
I am. I am.

100
00:08:11,585 --> 00:08:14,610
So you lost all these sales
and then what happened?

101
00:08:14,710 --> 00:08:16,610
Ruby! Don't play there. It's wet.

102
00:08:16,710 --> 00:08:17,910
Mum! Mum!

103
00:08:19,293 --> 00:08:21,460
I'm gonna smash its head!

104
00:08:24,543 --> 00:08:28,110
- Be careful.
- Mum, Mum! I'm gonna smash it.

105
00:08:30,502 --> 00:08:32,694
What would you like me
to do for Wednesday?

106
00:08:32,794 --> 00:08:36,294
I can get their birthday cakes.
That's easy.

107
00:08:37,794 --> 00:08:41,027
I was hoping Ruby would
change her mind.

108
00:08:41,836 --> 00:08:44,277
She doesn't want a joint
party with Sam this year.

109
00:08:44,377 --> 00:08:46,077
- Oh.
- Mum! Mum!

110
00:08:47,669 --> 00:08:49,152
She wants to have a princess party.

111
00:08:49,252 --> 00:08:50,452
Mum! Mum!

112
00:08:51,502 --> 00:08:52,702
That's OK.

113
00:08:53,002 --> 00:08:54,969
We don't have to come.

114
00:08:55,252 --> 00:08:57,019
You can still come.

115
00:08:57,211 --> 00:08:58,237
Mum!

116
00:08:58,337 --> 00:09:00,444
She just doesn't want to share
the day with Sam anymore.

117
00:09:00,544 --> 00:09:02,529
- I understand. I understand.
- Mum!

118
00:09:02,629 --> 00:09:05,329
